        <!-- Heading Row -->
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">

                <p class="description">This plugin downloads a diagram from Geodesign Hub and provides a way to buffer it and upload it back as a new diagram to the project. This project uses the <a href="https://www.geodesignhub.com/api/">Geodesign Hub API</a> and is opensource
